bpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999935807864, \"rank\": 6.419221961062577e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about 20 athletes\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1387}, {\"ngram\": \"37 medals\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1415}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"badminton\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"weightlifting\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1484}, {\"ngram\": \"a solitary silver\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"archery\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rifda hopes her Olympic debut will help raise the profile of a sport often overlooked in the Southeast Asian nation.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1615, \"end\": 1630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asia\", \"score\": 0.9999999982510417, \"rank\": 1.251225579669171e-09, \"text\": \"Southeast Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rifda\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic debut\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"the profile\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She jokes that knowledge about gymnastics in Indonesia is so limited that some people still think she does aerobics.\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1684, \"end\": 1693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"score\": 0.9998005050144723, \"rank\": 0.00013767281130967624, \"text\": \"Indonesia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"knowledge\", \"fr