sports school, said her daughter had fought through many challenges as a young athlete.\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2785, \"end\": 2793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andriana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andriana\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andriana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andriana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rifda's mother\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"a teacher\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2827}, {\"ngram\": \"a specialist sports school\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2857}, {\"ngram\": \"her daughter\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"many challenges\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2911}, {\"ngram\": \"a young athlete\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 2930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not afford expensive training and gymnastics clothes, so we always had to thrift for second-hand clothes,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 3058, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"expensive training and gymnastics clothes\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 2994}, {\"ngram\": \"second-hand clothes\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was sad, but it was all I could do.\\\"\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3099, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These days, she said, her daughter has been facing a different challenge.\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her daughter\", \"from\": 3123, \"to\": 3135}, {\"ngram\": \"a different challenge\", \"from\": 3152, \"to\": 3173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the world's most populous Muslim-majority nation, religious conservatives have recently harassed Rifda online, describing photos of her in leotards as \\\"pornographic\\\".\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3345, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world's most populous Muslim-majority nation\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3227}, {\"ngram\": \"religio